* Majid M. Naini, &quot;The Mysteries of the Universe and Rumi&#x27;s Discoveries on the Majestic Path of Love&quot;, Universal Vision &amp; Research, 2002, 
* Franklin Lewis, &quot;Rumi: Past and Present, East and West&quot;, Oneworld Publications, 2000. 
* Leslie Wines, &quot;Rumi: A Spiritual Biography&quot;, New York: Crossroads, 2001 .
* &quot;Rumi&#x27;s Thoughts&quot;, edited by Seyed G. Safavi, London: London Academy of Iranian Studies, 2003.
* William Chittick, &quot;The Sufi Doctrine of Rumi: Illustrated Edition&quot;, Bloomington: World Wisdom, 2005.
* Şefik Can, &quot;Fundamentals of Rumi&#x27;s Thought: A Mevlevi Sufi Perspective&quot;, Sommerset (NJ): The Light Inc., 2004, .
