* Waley, Muhammad Isa (2017). &quot;The Stanzaic Poems (Tarjī&#x27;āt) of Rumi&quot;. &quot;Critical Edition, Translation, and Commentary, with Additional Chapters on Aspects of His Divan&quot; (School of Oriental and African Studies, London).

